snippet.title: Cut the Rope 2 Official Game Trailer - Exclusively on the App Store
snippet.description: Cut the Rope 2 is available exclusively on the App Store http://bit.ly/1gG8CWT! Watch the video to see how Om Nom's unexpected adventure begins and get a sneak peek at some of the fantastic characters that Om Nom meets along the way! From the lush forest to the busy city, Om Nom's adventure has begun. Are you ready to join him?
